    <item>
      <title>Chris Hohn 的对冲基金 2023 年反弹 33%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/chris-hohn-s-hedge-fund-bounces-back-with-33-gain-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[激进投资者兼慈善家克里斯·霍恩 (Chris Hohn) 的基金去年飙升近 33%，创下四年来的最佳表现，远远领先于大多数对冲基金同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/chris-hohn-s-hedge-fund-bounces-back-with-33-gain-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:06:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权基金在保险公司的帮助下以自身名义借款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/apollo-s-athene-among-insurers-ramping-up-private-equity-lending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司（Apollo Global Management Inc.）处于这一日益增长的趋势的最前沿：保险公司向希望以其投资借款的私募股权基金提供贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/apollo-s-athene-among-insurers-ramping-up-private-equity-lending</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 16:18:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金乘势 2023 年市场反弹，老虎环球基金反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/tiger-global-hedge-fund-gained-29-in-2023-after-two-year-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tiger Global Management 结束了连续两年的下跌，2023 年上涨了 28.5%，超过了 Viking Global Investors 和 Coatue Management 等同行，这一年对传统选股者来说是强劲的一年。]]></description>
